{
  "stem": "11000.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "If one of the other prisoners knows-- knows that you carry a piece of bread on you, you're not gonna have it too long in your possession.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the end result was, when you get this little piece of bread, you-- you swallow it down as soon as you can.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you go hungry the rest of the day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then, you stand there with your little plate to get the soup, and you have to line up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you want to stand in front of the line, you take the chance to get the top of the barrel, which is nothing but just the water.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you go to the end of the line, many times by the time they get to you, there isn't any left, and you end up with nothing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you learn how to fight for your life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you try to squeeze in the middle and you hopefully you get some potato peels and some grass or whatever is in there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, it never was enough.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It never was sufficient.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I would say what was the worst experience in the concentration camp, it's very simple.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's hunger.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You're constantly hungry from the time you were there until we got out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's-- it's-- there was nothing you wouldn't do to get your hand on a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And even to this day, it's something that-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it's hard to explain.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "How can you explain to somebody what hunger is like?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] One day in Birkenau, this SS Oberscharfuhrer-- Otto Moll was his name-- he was a big heavy SS man.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he came, and he announced that if any of the prisoners in my barrack were-- had a trade, they should step forward.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
